31:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：AI Review 嘅準確度有幾高？"}]}]
32:["$","p",null,{"children":"對於明顯嘅問題（例如 null 檢查缺失、明顯邏輯錯誤、安全漏洞如 SQL injection）準確度高。對於業務邏輯嘅正確性、複雜嘅並發問題、性能調優，AI 嘅判斷需要人工驗證。把 AI review 當作有用嘅第一步，唔係最終裁決。"}]
33:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：可唔可以設定 AI 自動 approve 同 merge？"}]}]
34:["$","p",null,{"children":"技術上可以，但強烈唔建議。自動 merge 失去咗最後一道人工防線，一旦 AI 判斷出錯，錯誤代碼直接進入 main branch。最安全嘅設定係：AI 做 review、提建議，approve + merge 由人手確認。"}]
35:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：支唔支持 GitLab / Bitbucket？"}]}]
36:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"github"}]," Skill 係針對 GitHub 設計嘅。GitLab 同 Bitbucket 有各自嘅社區 Skill，但功能同成熟度可能唔同。在 ClawHub 搜尋 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"gitlab"}]," 或 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"bitbucket"}]," 可以找到相關 Skill，記得做安全審查先安裝。"]}]
